==Russian==
===Etymology===
From Slavic ''*zolto-'' (Old Church Slavonic [[злато]]), From Indo-European ''*ghəl-''.  Cognate with Ukrainian [[золото]], Belarusian [[золото]], Bulgarian [[злато]], Serbian [[злато]], Slovenian [[zlato]], Czech [[zlato]], Slovakian [[zlato]], Polish [[złoto]].  The IE root is also the source of Germanic ''*gulþa-'' (English [[gold]]).

